Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到  你竟然会深陷迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的灵兽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喰灵白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承它的土宫一家　真是碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我竟然有种羡慕的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  不管哪边  今日都得做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲  咆哮波
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…别打了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们…求求你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就由我来做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…爸爸他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生石…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭纲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…是我害死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手…所以害死了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谏山黄泉是受到杀生石的影响怨灵化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾狐的灵魂碎片  纯粹的妖力结晶体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦为人所获  在得到无限灵力的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会渐渐被啃噬掉灵魂  而化作怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后与九尾狐的怨念同化  开始毁灭世上的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谏山冥的事件可能也与杀生石有关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是真的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为我们将黄泉逼得太紧  她才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由  接受杀生石都是不可原谅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她则犯了这一禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…怎么会…怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死都做不到吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有特异点出现立刻报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室长  灵气压地图反应异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一观测班  第二观测班  全都沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有第三观测班发来灵气信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了不让我们发现行踪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即向第三观测班发出退避劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环境省  超自然灾害对策室处理班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭纲  出动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭纲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这样子去了也是送死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下定决心了就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话…父亲你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我太不成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  擅离职守
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御灵解放
